comments: Griffin (BKN) establishes himself by firming up in Wiggins' (GSW) path, and marginal contact occurs as he releases and rolls to the basket.
Curry (GSW) releases his off arm and makes marginal contact with Edwards (BKN) that does not affect his ability to defend.
As Edwards (BKN) jumps in front of Curry (GSW), Curry abnormally and overtly launches into Edwards (BKN) to create contact as he passes.
Edwards (BKN) cleanly blocks the ball before it hits the backboard.
Thompson (GSW) makes marginal body contact with Irving (BKN) on the perimeter, which he is able to move through and continue on his path to the basket.
Porter Jr. (GSW) legally contests Irving's (BKN) driving shot attempt and as Irving returns to the floor, incidental contact occurs.
Looney (GSW) and Griffin (BKN) engage and separate as incidental contact occurs during the rebound.
Johnson (BKN) briefly grasps and releases Wiggins' (GSW) jersey away from the rebound.
Johnson (BKN) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Edwards (BKN) and Wiggins (GSW) briefly engage and separate during the pick.
Curry (GSW) moves laterally into Irving's (BKN) path and initiates body contact, which affects Irving's SQBR.
Looney (GSW) dislodges Mills (BKN) from his position during the rebound.
Looney (GSW) makes marginal body contact with Irving (BKN) on the perimeter during his dribble.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that Irving (BKN) dislodged Thompson (GSW) prior to the ball being released on the throw-in and an Away-from-the-Play foul was assessed.
Irving (BKN) commits a take foul on Thompson (GSW).
Payton II (GSW) and Irving (BKN) briefly engage and separate as Payton II releases and steals the inbound pass.
